NAME: Accumulated negative changes derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated negative changes from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_CHNG_NGTV =
    CASE
        WHEN TKN_PSSSSN_DT > DATEADD(month,-3,DT_RFRNC)
        AND TKN_PSSSSN_DT < DT_RFRNC
        AND GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT_INTL_RCGNTN - CRRYNG_AMNT < 0             
        AND CLLTLR_RL_TYP = 1
        AND (BLNC_SHT_RCGNSD_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV_ASST_PSTN_TKN_PSSSSN_TYP = 13
        OR BLNC_SHT_RCGNSD_FNNCL_ASST_INSTRMNT_TKN_PSSSSN_TYP = 50 
        OR LNG_SCRTY_PSTN_PRDNTL_PRTFL_ASSGNMNT_ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN_FNNCL_ASSTS_ASSGNMNT_TKN_PSSSSN_TYP = 7)
        THEN GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT_INTL_RCGNTN - CRRYNG_AMNT
        ELSE 'N/A'
    END;

NAME: Accumulated coverage ratio derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated coverage ratio from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT =
    CASE
        WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 
            AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (14, 45, 6, 8, 73, 74) 
            THEN ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT / GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT

        WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 2 
            AND PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 
            AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (4, 41, 47, 7, 9) 
            THEN ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR / GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT

        WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 
            AND ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (77, 76, 9)
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 26 THEN ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT = ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT / GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 21 THEN ACCMLTD_CVRG_RT = (GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK + GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK) / GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
                END

        WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 2 
            AND PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 
            AND IMPRMNT_STTS = 0 
            THEN ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR / GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT
        
        ELSE NULL
    END;

NAME: Accumulated write-off derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Accumulated write-off from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET ACCMLTD_TTL_WRTFFS = 
  CASE
    WHEN GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT = 0 AND CRRYNG_AMNT = 0 THEN ACCMLTD_WRTFFS
    ELSE N/A
  END;

SET ACCMLTD_PRTL_WRTFFS = 
  CASE
    WHEN CRRYNG_AMNT <> 0 THEN ACCMLTD_WRTFFS
    ELSE N/A
  END;

NAME: Amounts derecognised for capital purposes derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Amounts derecognised for capital purposes from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET AMNT_DRCGNSD_CPTL_PRPS =

    WHEN SGNFCNT_RSK_TRNSFR_INDCTR = 1
    THEN CRRYNG_AMNT
    ELSE 'N/A'
  END;

NAME: Date/period of application of forbearance measure derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Date/period of application of forbearance measure from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET APPLCTN_FRBRNC_STTS_DT =

    WHEN DT_FRBRNC_MSRS > DATEADD(month,-3,DT_RFRNC) 
    AND DT_FRBRNC_MSRS < DT_RFRNC
    THEN 2
    ELSE -1
  END;

NAME: Derived default status derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Derived default status from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET DFLT_STTS_DRVD = 
  CASE
    WHEN /*INSTRMNT.*/DFLT_STTS IN (18, 19, 20)
    OR /*PRTY.*/DFLT_STTS IN (18, 19, 20)
    THEN 6
    ELSE 14
  END;

NAME: Gross carrying amount derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Gross carrying amount from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET GRSS_CRRYNG_AMNT = 
    CASE
        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (4, 41, 47, 7)
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 11 THEN FV
                    WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 THEN FV + ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR
                END

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (6, 8, 9)
            THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 77
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 26 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT 
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 211 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 212 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK
                END

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 9 
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 1 
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 26 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT 
                                WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 211 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_CRDT_RSK
                                WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 212 THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + GNRL_ALLWNCS_BNK_RSK
                            END

                    WHEN SBJCT_IMPRMNT_INDCTR = 2
                        THEN
                            CASE
                                WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 11 THEN FV
                                WHEN PRFRMNG_STTS = 1 THEN FV + ACCMLTD_CHNGS_FV_CR
                            END
                END

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (76, 73)
            THEN CRRYNG_AMNT

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN = 74 
            THEN CRRYNG_AMNT + ACCMLTD_IMPRMNT

        WHEN ACCNTNG_CLSSFCTN IN (2, 3)
            THEN FV
    END;

NAME: Time past due band derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Time past due band from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET TM_PST_DU = DT_PST_D - DT_RFRNC,
    TM_PST_DU_BND =
        CASE
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 0 THEN 0 
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 0 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 1/12 THEN 75
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 1/12 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 3/12 THEN 9
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 3/12 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 6/12 THEN 12
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 6/12 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 1 THEN 16
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 1 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 2 THEN 21
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 2 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 5 THEN 29
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 5 AND TM_PST_DU / 365 <= 7 THEN 84
            WHEN TM_PST_DU / 365 > 7 THEN 85
        END;

NAME: Time elapsed since initial recognition derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Time elapsed since initial recognition from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET TM_SNC_RCGNTN = DT_RFRNC - TKN_PSSSSN_DT,
    TM_SNC_INTL_RCGNTN = 
        CASE
            WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 > 0 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 <= 1 THEN 20
            WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 > 1 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 <= 2 THEN 27
            WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 > 2 AND TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 <= 5 THEN 29
            WHEN TM_SNC_RCGNTN / 365 > 5 THEN 37
        END;

NAME: Transfer between impairment stages derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Transfer between impairment stages from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET TRNSFR_IMPRMNT_STGS =
    CASE
        WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 23
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 24 THEN 3
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 25 THEN 5
                END

        WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 24
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 23 THEN 1
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 25 THEN 6
                END

        WHEN INTL_IMPRMNT_STTS = 25
            THEN
                CASE
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 23 THEN 2
                    WHEN IMPRMNT_STTS = 24 THEN 4
                END
    END;

NAME: Transferred amount derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Transferred amount from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM: SET BIRD_ASST_PL_INSTRMNT_ASSGNMNT_EIL.TRNSFRRD_AMNT = BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.NMNL_AMNT * BIRD_ASST_PL_INSTRMNT_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRCNTG_TRNSFRD

NAME: Aggregated commitment amount for Anacredit reporting derivation rule
DESCRIPTION: This derivation rule aims to obtain the Aggregated commitment amount for Anacredit reporting from its building blocks.
ALGORITHM:
SET BIRD_ENTTY_RL_EIL.AGGRGTD_CMMTMNT_AMNT_ANCRDT_RPRTNG =
CASE
    WHEN BIRD_PRTY_IL.PRTY_TYP NOT IN (18, 19)
    THEN
        (
            SELECT SUM(BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.NMNL_AMNT + BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.OFF_BLNC_SHT_AMNT)
            FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL
            WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
                      SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL.INSTRMNT_ID
                      FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL
                      WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL.INSTRMNT_RL_TYP IN (34, 35)
                  )
              AND (
                    (BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT = 80
                          AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
                          SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID
                          FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL
                          WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_ID = BIRD_PRTY_IL.PRTY_ID
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_RL_TYP = 4
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_TYP = 24
                                                
                   )
                  )
                  OR  
                    (BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT = 1020
                          AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
                          SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID
                          FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL
                          WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_ID = BIRD_PRTY_IL.PRTY_ID
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_RL_TYP = 4
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_TYP = 20
                                                
                   )
                  )
                                                              
                    OR
                    (BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT IN = 1022
                     AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
                          SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID
                          FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL
                          WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_ID = BIRD_PRTY_IL.PRTY_ID
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_RL_TYP = 28
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_TYP = 6
                     )
                    )
                    OR
                     (BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT = 1023
                     AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
                          SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ID
                          FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL
                          WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_ID = BIRD_PRTY_IL.PRTY_ID
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.PRTY_RL_TYP = 4
                            AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_TYP = 20
                     )
                    )
                    OR
                     (BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT = 51

NAME: Protection value type derivation rule

                )
                AND BIRD_CLLTRL_RL_IL.CLLTRL_RL_TYP = 1

                AND BIRD_SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV_IL.SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV_TYP IN

            (
                BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT = 2
                AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL.INSTRMNT_RL_TYP = 39
            )
        THEN 1

        WHEN

            )
            AND BIRD_CLLTRL_RL_IL.CLLTRL_RL_TYP = 1
            AND BIRD_CLLTRL_IL.MRKT_VL IS NOT NULL
        THEN 3

            BIRD_CLLTRL_IL.CLLTRL_TYP IN (

            )

            AND BIRD_CLLTRL_IL.MRKT_VL IS NULL
            AND BIRD_CLLTRL_IL.LT_SSTNBL_VL IS NOT NULL

            )

                AND BIRD_SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV_IL.SCRTY_EXCHNG_TRDBL_DRVTV_TYP NOT IN

            )
            OR
            (
                BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL.INSTRMNT_RL_TYP = 39
                AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT IN (
                    12, 511, 512, 522, 51, 80, 1022, 13, 14
                )
            )
            OR
            (
                BIRD_INSTRMNT_RL_IL.INSTRMNT_RL_TYP IN (
                    39, 6, 38
                )
                AND BIRD_INSTRMNT_IL.INSTRMNT_TYP_PRDCT IN (
                    5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 380
                )
            )
        THEN 4

        ELSE 5
    END;

NAME: ANCRDT_INSTRMNT_C generation rule
DESCRIPTION: This generation rule aims to describe the generation of ANCRDT_INSTRMNT_C table within BIRD.
ALGORITHM:
SET ANCRDT_INSTRMNT_C.INSTRMNT_ID = BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID
WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
    SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID
    FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL
    JOIN BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_EIL
      ON BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID = BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID
    JOIN BIRD_ENTTY_RL_EIL
      ON BIRD_ENTTY_RL_EIL.PRTY_ID = BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_EIL.PRTY_ID
    WHERE BIRD_ENTTY_RL_EIL.AGGRGTD_CMMTMNT_AMNT_ANCRDT_RPRTNG >= 25000
);

NAME: ANCRDT_JNT_LBLTS_C generation rule
DESCRIPTION: This generation rule aims to describe the generation of ANCRDT_JNT_LBLTS_C table within BIRD.
ALGORITHM:
SET ANCRDT_JNT_LBLTS_C.INSTRMNT_ID = BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID 
WHERE BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID IN (
    SELECT BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID
    FROM BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL

      ON BIRD_INSTRMNT_ENTTY_RL_ASSGNMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID = BIRD_INSTRMNT_EIL.INSTRMNT_ID
